    <Feat>
      <Name>Past Life: Monk - Dragon Disciple</Name>
      <Description>You were a Dragon Disciple in a past life. Others find you strangely compelling
when you speak or take to the battlefield. Each time you acquire this feat you
gain +1 Attack and -1 to the Spell Point cost of the Maximize Metamagic.
This feat can be stacked up to three times.</Description>
      <MaxTimesAcquire>3</MaxTimesAcquire>
      <Acquire>HeroicPastLife</Acquire>
      <Icon>PastLifeMonk</Icon>
